high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the wall and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the potato off of the counter.
Walk around the counter to the kitchen sink.
Wash the potato in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the clean potato on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick the potato up from the counter.
Go left and then right to stand at the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the potato.
Move the left and face the counter to the left of the toaster.
Put the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the black stools, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn left and walk along the counter, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the potato in the sink.
Place the potato on the counter in front of and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed potato on a counter.
